<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "FAQ:" [1-21] -->
<h2 class="sectionedit2"><a name="when_i_run_gusanos_on_fullscreen_i_get_this_error_unhandled_exceptioncouldn_t_set_graphics_mode" id="when_i_run_gusanos_on_fullscreen_i_get_this_error_unhandled_exceptioncouldn_t_set_graphics_mode">When I run Gusanos on fullscreen I get this error “Unhandled exception: Couldn’t set graphics mode”</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Something on your PC doesnt support the 320&times;240 resolution. The fast and sure way to fix this problem is to run gusanos on double res mode, to do this add “double” at the bottom of the <a href="doku.php?id=main:general_docs:faq:usage:general:config" class="wikilink1" title="main:general_docs:faq:usage:general:config">config.cfg</a> file. However, double res mode is a bit slower and there is a chance that updating your video drivers will fix the problem, so you should also try that. Changing the operating systems&#039; video resolution can also help.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "When I run Gusanos on fullscreen I get this error “Unhandled exception: Couldn’t set graphics mode”" [22-] --></div>
